{"tid":2437886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨史專家：中共91種革命精神","createTime":"2021-03-08T07:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T07:11:40.000Z","uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d77d6f29cf193fd15a13c50814c606e2c82958b1","tid":2437886,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:08:05.000Z","msg":"今年是中共建黨百年。全國政協委員、中央黨史和文獻研究院原副院長吳德剛昨天在回答記者提問時說，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">過去幾年，黨史院研究梳理了中國共產黨人在不同時期地區和領域形成的革命精神，總共有九十一種，「我們還要繼續研究和梳理。」 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&emsp;&emsp;吳德剛說，我們深刻體會到，革命精神是黨的寶貴財富。大家耳熟能詳的焦裕祿精神、王傑精神、雷鋒精神、鐵人精神，都是我們不斷前行的動力。他表示，一個國家一個民族不能沒有靈魂，一個政黨一刻也離不開精神的滋養。從井岡山精神、長征精神、延安精神、抗美援朝精神到新時代偉大的抗疫精神、脫貧攻堅精神，都展現了共產黨人的偉大品格。<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/2339429/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%B2%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B191%E7%A8%AE%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F2339429%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B191%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058teKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=79ffd966\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F2339429%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B191%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E&h=b196e6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/2339429/%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%B2%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B191%E7%A8%AE%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=